---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Dog-Friendly Itineraries in London — A Dog's Guide"
description: "Full-day and half-day dog-friendly London itineraries — planned routes with stops, timings and venue ratings."
footerType: london
permalink: /london/itineraries/
---

<div class="dest-intro">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="dest-breadcrumb">
      <a href="/london/"><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></i> London</a>
      <span>›</span> Itineraries
    </p>
    <h1>Itineraries</h1>
    <p class="dest-intro-desc">Planned routes for a full day out with your dog — stops, timings and venue ratings included.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="venue-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="venue-list">
      {% for itinerary in london_itineraries %}
      <a href="/london/itineraries/{{ itinerary.slug }}/" class="dest-subpage-card">
        <div class="dest-subpage-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-route" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
        <h3>{{ itinerary.title }}</h3>
        <span class="dest-card-link">View route</span>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
